{
  "name": "RPlog_Hunting_Kyokusha_and_Thrask",
  "title": "The Hunt Through Old Mos Eisley",
  "summary": "Reneging on a promise for the Imperial bounty, Danik Kreldin coordinates a hunt for the fugitive Kyokusha through the slums of Old Mos Eisley, aided by the sniper Sandor Woden and the scarred soldier Sethas. Spotted by Sandor, Kyo is snatched off the street by Danik's swoop, but bites free and flees into the alleys, where a running firefight ensues; she wounds both Danik and Sethas with her blaster before Danik's pistol shot and Sandor's stun blast finally drop her unconscious. As Danik carries her off toward his ship the Vendetta, her ally Thrask the Quarren arrives too late, enraged, and battles Sethas and Sandor with blaster and sword, gravely wounding Sethas before Danik returns and knocks Thrask out with his ship's tractor beam. With both captives stun-cuffed and his men treated with bacta aboard the strike cruiser Broadsword, Danik visits the imprisoned Kyokusha and Thrask en route to Imperial Corellia, coldly refusing Kyo's pleas to release her and intending to hand both criminals over to the proper authorities for the reward that will clear his debts.",
